Comment: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,成神阳太先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你说自己是研究所派来的实验助手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这其实是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请你立刻离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不通报警方已经是对你的宽容了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能再见到雏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那孩子预计要转移去国外的机构
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,比这里更先进的机构
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因此  你应该无法再和她见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:00:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,至少今天让我和雏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,成神先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就算只有半…半天也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,时间就只剩下今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能一起玩的时间  也到今天为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让你打开心扉的  只有游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雏没有我的话  不会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是几呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.12,Comment,,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说这是最后的学习时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至少回答我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让我知道你没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那我无论如何都会把你带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你一定要答应我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意离开这里  和我一起生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去年夏天  雏是和我一起度过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,身边环绕着家人和许多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想不起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是记不起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,每一天明明是那么的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说这里的生活更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,空…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对  是空  答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那这个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,和空相反  支撑着脚底的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,土?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜  是更大一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那这个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是意味着时间的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,时间  也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,时子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我找找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是白天天上会有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是在燃烧的星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:03:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…再给我点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再多一点点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能就这样回…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要带上雏一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,带上雏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大家  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没能把雏夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的归属就在那里了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥跟你说再见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雏也要跟他说再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,少了?  什么少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,阳艾不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不能没有阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小雏  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,阳…艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,西欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候的情感  还残留着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在也互相喜欢着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没有察觉到这种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,连这种感情我都没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,雏喜欢阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢阳艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,司波小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她选择了能让自己幸福的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,回到我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的公主殿下回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  阳太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  现在的雏已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的表情就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥  该出手时就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,令我刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感谢这个温暖的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对于大家也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,剪头发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点不甘心  但还挺可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她以前一直穿的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那个就一点都不像雏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那个电影就不能继续拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要穿那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么鬼  天愿小姐居然赞同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思  我就这么扭曲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,即便雏已经变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大家还是想延续那个夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凭我的人脉  随随便便就能定制一套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,录影里可以确认衣服具体是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没碰这个要来一发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,听好哦  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿进那个环里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从下往上扔就可以了  用全力扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  相遇的时候她也是先对这个感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和雏相遇之后做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全部是雏想要作为普通人体验的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,打篮球  吃拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,作为家庭的一员一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也会想要做一次电影的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个夏天充满了雏想要做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然想要遗忘那么重要的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那扔扔看吧  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,扔多少次都没关系  直到扔进去为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好  就着这个势头再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先不要动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  尺码合不合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好  最后戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  穿好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然头发稍微短了点  但是和那时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以重新开始拍摄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那首先是笔直地从神殿走过去的场景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,预备  开机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雏  你只要走到这里来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雏  你是这个故事的女主角哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我演和你一起的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,之前拍过我们主演的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是拍电影的后续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  朝这里走过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只要抬头挺胸的走过来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会一直等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的就好  过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样  到这边来  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,卡  过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的名演员来演  肯定是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛电影一般呢  到现在我们经历的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,平凡的我邂逅了自称为神的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,解决了各种的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一起度过了一个夏天  然后恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然也有困难  但都克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,像现在这样  两个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互相选择了对方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以像现在这样在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定了  我要重新考大学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成为像雏的爷爷一样优秀学者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命学习雏所得的病的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的力量帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,若是还没有人研究出来的话  我来研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是人类的智惠无法涉及的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会去开辟道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这样一来  雏就要和我一直在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雏  喜欢  阳太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  自信涌现出来了  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么目标都没有  只是碌碌活着的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有了想要做的事  充满了干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的感觉有生以来还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为我指明了人生道路的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或许真的是我的神明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,卡  杀青
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,努力到最后真了不起  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等制作好了来个上映会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这之后还有很多要做的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,选曲是伊座并同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,负责照明的你没事了吧  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我待到最后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天结束了  到了微感寒意的三月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  阳太要复读了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,先冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你都考上八幡大学了  不去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,本来我一开始考也是动机不纯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且现在找到了想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你去  我们换下名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让我去整容也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  下面开始上映会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雏  我们的电影完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雏是你想演女主角的电影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雏出演到了最后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接下来要看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  开始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,世界面临着危机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,人们把这种无法解释的灾害称为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,『世界的破绽』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还没调查出来吗  世界的破绽的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在魔术师们正在拼命调查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还请您再等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,王啊  这就是世界的大脑  SYSTEM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然而它的能源已经枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一个个的回路都开始停止运作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以导致各地发生了灾害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,应当将国内的精灵使召集起来组成调查团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这精灵的数量是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安  你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么光着脚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我马上要去王都了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天长老和我这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只说了拯救世界的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然残酷  但那是永远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,永远是指直到死为止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么一定是安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,歌也唱的不好  也比较笨拙  没有什么才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有拯救世界的能力是出类拔萃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,找机会把安带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两个人远走高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的终结什么的  与我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是要牺牲安的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,把安作为活祭品  拯救世界的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,安就这样  向着祭坛走去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没有才能也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢安  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就让这仪式结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快把他赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  仪式被…  回路已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,维持世界的系统要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,世界要崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒啊  完全就是杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小雏是女星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  这样可赢不了她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,导演的水平也很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是大家美好的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有那样的东西的话  人就能很幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真的是很美好的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧  雏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那开始拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是花絮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小雏叫我把这个加在最后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  这次当了一回神有什么感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  一切都是那么新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,每一天都亮闪闪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回忆化为一颗颗宝石  填满了好大一个宝石箱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就算世界终结了  一切都毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这回忆是不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是我永远的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:22:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  你是这样想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今后要面对的未来无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会非常无助  奇迹也不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是非常残酷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,和雏一起活下去
Comment: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（完结不撒花。）
